{"tid":1423954,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"歡迎舉報犯法商店","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T00:20:13.000Z","uid":94277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e1a9280f57dcb8110431439ca9fadd6d2a2ee45e","tid":1423954,"uid":94277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:09:16.000Z","msg":"為保障香港市民人身安全, 鼓勵市民舉報所有販賣攻擊性武器的店舖<br />\n攻擊性武器例如: 18CM長鐳射槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4b965adf9da9bb24927fdd6836ca21e66f0ca8","tid":1423954,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:19:03.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6f4cee3e496ba184e44e593f621885aeee952546","tid":1423954,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:21:19.000Z","msg":"街市好多刀賣 我要舉報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n福建幫拎刀斬人唔撚理<br />\n買支電筒就走去捉<br />\n班狗有幾得閒"},{"pid":"451746478905a19faf9f806c1709a40c26786936","tid":1423954,"uid":94277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:03:08.000Z","msg":"聽日去深水埗做資料搜集<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9bac2fc909a1c1222560a8df439c3b7c55a5100","tid":1423954,"uid":288849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:20:13.000Z","msg":"文宣商戰：撐「五大訴求、缺一不可」良心認證標誌店舖消費推廣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438675</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}